review_text:
Posted: November 3
|why is it always...?| |fingers|

Great "story-", but poor "-telling", horrible questing;
Great gameplay, but lots of outdated, clumsy and inconvenient aspects;
Great world to explore, but it will begin to feel empty and dull as soon as the slapping veil of beauty comes off.

Therefore the game is in a superposition - it sends greetings from the 2000s with disgusting gameplay solutions, but at the same time sets the standard for the genre in the big 2020s.

